snippet.title: Tiny Archers VR – Artemis smart bow support announcement (Upload VR Winter Showcase 2023 Trailer)
snippet.description:
Tiny Archers VR – Adam's Tale will provide full support for the Artemis smart bow from day one. This is the announcement trailer!

EARLY ACCESS now available on the Meta Quest App Lab (Quest 2/Pro/3):
https://www.meta.com/experiences/5072443666191114/
